*************************************VALUE ASSESSMENT (kople til Kahneman og pleasure by estimation=confidence)
<block test>
/ trials = [1=ValueScale]
</block>

**
<shape blank2>
/ shape = rectangle
/ color = white
/ size = (100%, 100%)
</shape>

Fikse slik at alt blir lagra som 0 til 100 i valuescale. sjekk orrige skript! og maxscale osv..
*VALUE SCALE VERTICAL AND INTEGRATED:
trial ValueScaleTest>
/ ontrialbegin = [if (values.numberofbuttonadjust==0 && values.numberofmouseadjust==0) values.predtimer=script.elapsedtime]
/ stimulusframes = [1=linestarter, linesize, proportionscorevalue]
/ inputdevice = mouse
/ validresponse = (lineVERT, continuetxtVERT)
/ correctresponse= (continuetxtVERT)
/ branch = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0) trial.ValueScale]
/ontrialend = [values.valuescaleresponsey=trial.ValueScale.responsey]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.response=="lineVERT") values.valuescalelastresponse=expressions.actualscorevalue]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0) values.vpositionAvalueVERT=expressions.tuneposVERT]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0 && trial.ValueScale.response=="lineVERT") values.numberofmouseadjust=values.numberofmouseadjust+1]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) values.predtimer= script.elapsedtime-values.predtimer]
/ branch =[if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) trial.savevaluedata]
</trial>


<trial ValueScale>
/ ontrialbegin = [if (values.numberofmouseadjust==0) values.predtimer=script.elapsedtime]
/ stimulusframes = [1=bildeein, bildeto, bildetre, continuetxtVERT, lineVERT, XVERT,
valuepredictionoutcometxt, valuepredictionoutcometxt2, valuepredictionoutcometxt3, feelingtxt]
/ inputdevice = mouse
/ validresponse = (lineVERT, continuetxtVERT)
/ correctresponse= (continuetxtVERT)
/ branch = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0) trial.ValueScale]
/ontrialend = [values.valuescaleresponsey=trial.ValueScale.responsey]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.response=="lineVERT") values.valuescalelastresponse=expressions.actualscorevalue]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0) values.vpositionAvalueVERT=expressions.tuneposVERT]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==0 && trial.ValueScale.response=="lineVERT") values.numberofmouseadjust=values.numberofmouseadjust+1]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) values.predtimer= script.elapsedtime-values.predtimer]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) values.valueoutcome=values.lastresponsefixed]
/ ontrialend = [if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) values.valueprediction=values.lastlatency]
/ branch =[if (trial.ValueScale.correct==1) trial.savevaluedata]
</trial>

<trial ValueScale2>
/ ontrialbegin = [if (values.numberofmouseadjust==0) values.predtimer=script.elapsedtime]
/ stimulusframes = [1=bildeein, bildeto, bildetre, continuetxtVERT, lineVERT, XVERT,
valuepredictionoutcometxtreaction, valuepredictionoutcometxt2, valuepredictionoutcometxt3, feelingtxt2]
